Usage: SET FAKE_HOST <some text>
  This text is displayed instead of your actual hostname in a CTCP
  FINGER reply.

  This is useful for dialup users with dynamic IPs, as it allows them
  to display their actual email address.

See Also:
  SET USE_FAKE_HOST
  CTCP FINGER
